sdp/implementation-plan.md:1:# PRD: CypherClaw Humanization — Structured Expression Rendering Layer — Implementation Plan
sdp/implementation-plan.md:18:- **T-001** [T1] Build a rule-ablation debugger that re-renders a score with selected rules disabled to localize expressive problems. (~3h)
sdp/implementation-plan.md:20:- **T-003** [T1] Implement R1 Metric Accent: per-beat-position velocity multiplier applied only to non-grid-locked melodic/accent voices. (~3h)
sdp/implementation-plan.md:21:- **T-004** [T1] Implement R2 Phrase Arch (Todd/KTH): parabolic tempo + loudness arch over each phrase, modulated by section envelope. (~3h)
sdp/implementation-plan.md:22:- **T-005** [T1] Implement R3 Agogic Accent: lengthen + emphasize notes at local contour apex or harmonic-charge peak. (~3h)
sdp/implementation-plan.md:23:- **T-006** [T1] Implement R4 Duration Contrast: exaggerate short-vs-long by log(dur_ratio_to_median), melodic roles only, capped at ±10%. (~3h)
sdp/implementation-plan.md:24:- **T-007** [T1] Implement R5 Final Ritardando: Friberg–Sundberg square-root tempo curve over last 20–30% of cadential phrases. (~3h)
sdp/implementation-plan.md:25:- **T-008** [T1] Implement R6 Punctuation + Breath: lengthen terminal note at phrase boundary and insert breath silence of breath_after_ms. (~3h)
sdp/implementation-plan.md:26:- **T-009** [T1] Implement R7 Articulation Shaping: per-note gate-time by style (legato 0.95–1.02, normal 0.7–0.85, staccato 0.3–0.5, staccatissimo 0.15–0.25) with contour adjustments. (~3h)
sdp/implementation-plan.md:27:- **T-010** [T1] Implement R8 Microtiming Polish: per-note Gaussian jitter σ=3 ms on melodic, 1 ms on ostinato, 0 ms on grid-locked machine voices. (~3h)
sdp/implementation-plan.md:35:- **T-011** [T1] Implement R12 Sensor-to-Intent Aggregation Matrix: smoothed IIR + hysteresis → aggregate intentions (global_energy, global_restraint, global_brightness). (~3h) → deps: T-001
sdp/implementation-plan.md:36:- **T-012** [T1] Implement bounded reactive delta track in scheduler with per-parameter modulation caps. (~3h) → deps: T-001
sdp/implementation-plan.md:40:- **T-016** [T1] Implement performance-worm logger: 2D trajectory in tempo–loudness space + convex-hull area computation as CI artifact. (~3h) → deps: T-001
sdp/implementation-plan.md:52:- **T-021** [T1] Implement R9 Motif Memory: LRU cache of motif hashes with variation menu and return-home decay. (~3h) → deps: T-011
sdp/implementation-plan.md:53:- **T-022** [T1] Implement R10 Silence Budget: per-voice and per-section accumulators enforced at phrase boundaries. (~3h) → deps: T-011
sdp/implementation-plan.md:54:- **T-023** [T1] Implement wind/voice lung-capacity constraints: 4–8 s continuous-play cap per instrument-sim voice. (~3h) → deps: T-011
sdp/implementation-plan.md:55:- **T-024** [T1] Implement R11 Call-Response Gating: follower phrase intent complements leader's realized performance. (~3h) → deps: T-011
sdp/implementation-plan.md:57:- **T-026** [T1] Implement tempo-dependent swing curve per Friberg/Sundström (3.5:1 at slow tempi down toward 1:1 at fast), with short-note near-constant ~100 ms. (~3h) → deps: T-011
sdp/implementation-plan.md:59:- **T-028** [T1] Implement restraint parameter enforced as global dampener across rules. (~3h) → deps: T-011
sdp/implementation-plan.md:67:- **T-029** [T1] Implement the Event dataclass with score-level, performance-level, reactive-delta, and provenance fields. (~3h) → deps: T-001
sdp/implementation-plan.md:68:- **T-030** [T1] Implement PerformanceIntent per-phrase metadata with arc shape, deviation bounds, tension target, restraint, and call/response role. (~3h) → deps: T-001
sdp/implementation-plan.md:69:- **T-031** [T1] Implement SectionEnvelope with breakpoint functions over tempo_base, density_target, dynamic_plane, brightness, tension_trajectory. (~3h) → deps: T-001
sdp/implementation-plan.md:72:- **T-034** [T1] Implement seeded-RNG architecture with per-stage sub-seeds derived from a root seed along a seed_path tuple. (~3h) → deps: T-001
sdp/implementation-plan.md:85:- **T-040** [T2] Establish listener-review workflow: weekly rendered pieces tagged with rule-stack provenance, ablation tooling documented for operators, review log template in place. (~6h)
